org.jsonurl

Interface JsonTextBuilder<A,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - Accumulator type
    R - Result type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonUrlStringBuilder, JsonUrlTextAppender

    public interface JsonTextBuilder<A,R>
    A JSONURLBuilder builds JSON text.

    This interface implements the builder pattern.

    Since:
    2019-09-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
